1
00:00:14,567 --> 00:00:20,200
Can you sleep while in pain
because you're mad at her?

2
00:00:20,267 --> 00:00:22,033
You won't understand
where I'm coming from.

3
00:00:22,100 --> 00:00:24,133
Because you didn't get hurt.

4
00:00:24,200 --> 00:00:27,933
And you have no idea how
it feels to get betrayed

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,633
by your own child.

6
00:00:29,700 --> 00:00:31,600
This is going to be your room,
okay?

7
00:00:31,667 --> 00:00:33,500
You'll stay in the guest room.

8
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:35,700
Mom, can't she stay in my room?

9
00:00:35,767 --> 00:00:37,600
So I can look after her.

10
00:00:37,667 --> 00:00:41,567
I don't think it's proper
for you to stay in one room

11
00:00:41,633 --> 00:00:43,400
when you're not married yet.

12
00:00:43,467 --> 00:00:46,300
She took my son from me
when she killed him.

13
00:00:46,367 --> 00:00:51,200
So now I'm going to take her
daughter away from her.

14
00:00:51,267 --> 00:00:55,867
Until the day she loses
her daughter for good.

15
00:00:55,933 --> 00:01:00,733
I think I'll be happier
if my mom is here.

16
00:01:00,800 --> 00:01:04,333
Let's give your mom time
to absorb everything.

17
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:05,767
I'm sure the time will come,

18
00:01:05,833 --> 00:01:09,367
and she'll realize she can't
abandon you.

19
00:01:09,467 --> 00:01:11,633
Amanda, I talked to Eden
earlier.

20
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:13,067
Do you know where she is
right now?

21
00:01:13,133 --> 00:01:14,767
I don't care.

22
00:01:14,833 --> 00:01:16,333
She's at Rina's house.

23
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,467
Red took her there.

24
00:01:17,533 --> 00:01:18,500
What?

25
00:01:18,567 --> 00:01:19,667
How did that happen?

26
00:01:19,733 --> 00:01:21,900
I had to order something online
to make him happy.

27
00:01:21,967 --> 00:01:23,100
Why would you do that, Auntie?

28
00:01:23,167 --> 00:01:25,433
Is there an occasion?

29
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:26,900
No, actually, it's for Eden.

30
00:01:26,967 --> 00:01:28,467
She's staying with us.

31
00:01:28,533 --> 00:01:29,533
What?

32
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:32,800
Mom, I can't deny Red
of his right.

33
00:01:32,867 --> 00:01:35,267
My family accepted us.

34
00:01:35,333 --> 00:01:37,933
This is all your fault!

35
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,767
Mom, don't hurt him.

36
00:01:40,833 --> 00:01:41,767
- You bastard!
- Mom, please, stop.

37
00:01:41,833 --> 00:01:43,167
This is your fault!

38
00:01:43,233 --> 00:01:44,733
It's all your fault!

39
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,767
You and your mom!

40
00:01:46,833 --> 00:01:48,367
You're all the same!

41
00:01:48,433 --> 00:01:49,500
First, you ruined my life.

42
00:01:49,567 --> 00:01:52,000
And now, you're going to ruin my
daughter's life too!

43
00:01:53,133 --> 00:01:55,500
Mom, please stop.

44
00:01:55,567 --> 00:01:58,433
Don't drag us into your fight
with Miss Rina.

45
00:01:58,500 --> 00:01:59,833
Come with me.

46
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:01,500
Let's end this. Come with me.

47
00:02:01,567 --> 00:02:03,733
Come on, Dear. Let's go.

48
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:06,900
What do you mean
she's staying here?

49
00:02:06,967 --> 00:02:08,433
Did you approve that?

50
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:11,233
I mean, what is happening?

51
00:02:11,300 --> 00:02:12,767
I've no choice.

52
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:16,400
Eden is pregnant.

53
00:02:17,533 --> 00:02:18,700
What?

54
00:02:19,367 --> 00:02:20,967
Auntie, are you serious?

55
00:02:23,233 --> 00:02:25,433
Ma'am Rina! Someone's making
a scene outside.

56
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:26,500
Who?

57
00:02:28,833 --> 00:02:29,800
- Yen.
- Stay out of this!

58
00:02:29,867 --> 00:02:31,933
- Yen, let's go inside.
- Come with me.

59
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,267
Let go of my daughter.

60
00:02:33,333 --> 00:02:34,433
Yen, let's go inside.

61
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:35,567
Let's go. Come on.

62
00:02:35,633 --> 00:02:36,833
No!

63
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:38,167
She's coming with me.

64
00:02:40,967 --> 00:02:42,400
- Yen.
- Open the gate!

65
00:02:42,467 --> 00:02:44,000
What's going on?

66
00:02:44,067 --> 00:02:46,900
Oh, my God! Yen!

67
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,400
- What's going on?
- Yen!

68
00:02:48,467 --> 00:02:50,467
Let's bring her
to the hospital!

69
00:02:55,833 --> 00:02:57,100
I didn't mean to do that.

70
00:02:57,167 --> 00:02:57,867
You didn't mean
to do that?

71
00:02:57,933 --> 00:02:59,267
Get out of here!

72
00:02:59,333 --> 00:03:00,833
- What are you doing here?
- Wake up!

73
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:03,133
Yen!
Mom, she's unconscious!

74
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:05,900
Come on, let's bring her
to the hospital!

75
00:03:05,967 --> 00:03:06,933
I'm coming with you!

76
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,033
You can't come with us!

77
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:09,333
You're not going anywhere!

78
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:11,200
- I'm coming with you!
- You're not going anywhere.

79
00:03:11,267 --> 00:03:12,233
I want to come with you, Red!

80
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:13,267
No!

81
00:03:13,333 --> 00:03:15,633
You're such a pest, Amanda!

82
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:16,800
Go on, Red!

83
00:03:16,867 --> 00:03:18,767
Hurry!

84
00:03:18,833 --> 00:03:20,067
Hurry up!

85
00:03:21,733 --> 00:03:24,000
- Red, I'm coming with you!
- Get away!

86
00:03:25,833 --> 00:03:27,200
See what you have done?

87
00:03:27,267 --> 00:03:28,367
My daughter needs me!

88
00:03:28,433 --> 00:03:30,000
She doesn't need you!

89
00:03:30,067 --> 00:03:31,167
She doesn't need
you anymore!

90
00:03:31,233 --> 00:03:32,667
Remember that, Amanda!

91
00:03:32,733 --> 00:03:34,167
That's what you've done!

92
00:03:35,633 --> 00:03:38,133
If you can't accept
what happened,

93
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:41,533
don't you ever try to harm
my future grandchild!

94
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:43,200
I don't give a damn about you!

95
00:03:44,867 --> 00:03:47,267
If something bad happens
to my grandchild, Amanda...

96
00:03:47,333 --> 00:03:52,833
remember this, I will bring you
back to the hell you came from!

97
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:54,967
Do whatever you want!

98
00:03:55,067 --> 00:04:00,133
But I'll make sure to get my
daughter away from your family!

99
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,433
Get out of my property!

100
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:03,267
Get out!

101
00:04:03,333 --> 00:04:07,100
If you don't want to get hurt,
Amanda, get out of here!

102
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,800
Guard!

103
00:04:10,867 --> 00:04:11,900
Guard!

104
00:04:12,767 --> 00:04:14,767
Make her go away!

105
00:04:14,833 --> 00:04:15,800
Guard!

106
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:18,633
Make her leave!

107
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:23,933
Go home.

108
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:26,400
Get her out of here.

109
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,233
Don't touch me.

110
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:45,367
I didn't mean to hurt you.

111
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,467
I didn't mean to do that.

112
00:04:50,933 --> 00:04:52,900
I didn't mean to hurt you, Eden.

113
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:57,100
Thank you.

114
00:04:57,167 --> 00:04:59,367
Hello?
Yes, Victor.

115
00:04:59,433 --> 00:05:01,333
Sabina and I just got here
in the hospital.

116
00:05:01,433 --> 00:05:03,267
Yes, you don't need
to come here.

117
00:05:03,333 --> 00:05:05,733
I'll take care of everything,
okay?

118
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,033
Yes, I'll update you.

119
00:05:07,933 --> 00:05:11,367
Auntie, I still can't believe
that Red got Yeynyen pregnant.

120
00:05:11,433 --> 00:05:16,433
We wouldn't have this problem
if you didn't neglect my son.

121
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:17,967
Plus, I don't have to be
pretending

122
00:05:18,033 --> 00:05:20,333
that I like that Eden.

123
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:22,767
Auntie, if you're just
pretending,

124
00:05:22,833 --> 00:05:24,600
then why bother coming here?

125
00:05:24,667 --> 00:05:26,367
You should have just stayed
at home.

126
00:05:26,433 --> 00:05:28,400
And wait there for an update.

127
00:05:28,467 --> 00:05:32,733
I have to convince Red and Eden
that I really care.

128
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:38,500
And besides, I want to know
if Eden still has the baby.

129
00:05:40,233 --> 00:05:42,533
What do you mean, Auntie?

130
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:48,800
If Eden loses the baby,
she will blame Amanda for it.

131
00:05:48,867 --> 00:05:52,167
She'll lose the baby, and her
relationship with her mom

132
00:05:52,233 --> 00:05:53,333
will be ruined.

133
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:57,000
Things will go my way without
putting in an effort.

134
00:05:57,067 --> 00:05:58,033
Right?

135
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,667
Hello?

136
00:06:30,733 --> 00:06:32,333
Dindi.

137
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:34,000
I'm at the hospital now.

138
00:06:35,033 --> 00:06:36,667
Yes, I followed Rina here.

139
00:06:36,733 --> 00:06:40,367
But I don't know where
they're going.

140
00:06:40,867 --> 00:06:42,333
Just calm down, Amanda.

141
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:47,200
You must patch things up
with Eden.

142
00:06:47,967 --> 00:06:50,633
This is all my fault.

143
00:07:00,767 --> 00:07:01,733
How's Eden?

144
00:07:04,267 --> 00:07:05,533
She's still unconscious, Mom.

145
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,633
According to Dr. Villegas,

146
00:07:08,700 --> 00:07:10,600
she's in shock
because of the trauma.

147
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,100
How's the baby?

148
00:07:18,833 --> 00:07:19,567
Red!

149
00:07:19,633 --> 00:07:20,733
- How's our baby?
- Yen!

150
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,233
Stay still.

151
00:07:22,300 --> 00:07:23,333
Just rest for now.

152
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,367
How's our baby doing?
I'm okay.

153
00:07:25,433 --> 00:07:26,600
I want to know how
our baby's doing.

154
00:07:26,667 --> 00:07:28,300
Relax, relax.
Yen, please.

155
00:07:40,133 --> 00:07:42,533
You should talk to Eden.

156
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:47,200
I'm sure she'll understand that
it was an accident.

157
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:48,300
We both know Eden.

158
00:07:48,367 --> 00:07:52,667
She'll talk to you
no matter what happens.

159
00:07:52,733 --> 00:07:57,333
I hope she's doing okay.

160
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,733
I have to go.

161
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:02,133
I need to go to the airport.

162
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:04,100
Keep in touch, okay?

163
00:08:04,167 --> 00:08:05,067
Okay.

164
00:08:05,133 --> 00:08:06,100
Okay, bye.

165
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:11,100
Doctor, how is my baby doing?

166
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,500
The baby is fine, Eden.

167
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:17,000
Thank God our baby's okay.

168
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:22,567
I must say that you were
in a critical condition.

169
00:08:22,667 --> 00:08:24,333
You had profuse bleeding.

170
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:26,600
And like I said before,

171
00:08:26,667 --> 00:08:29,767
you should avoid strenuous
activities

172
00:08:29,833 --> 00:08:31,733
for your baby's welfare.

173
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:36,800
It was an accident, Doc.

174
00:08:36,867 --> 00:08:38,167
You're fine for now, Eden.

175
00:08:38,233 --> 00:08:40,467
We were able to control
the bleeding.

176
00:08:40,533 --> 00:08:44,300
But you almost lost the baby.

177
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,933
Eden, you almost had
a miscarriage

178
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,233
because of what happened.

179
00:08:50,567 --> 00:08:54,500
And I cannot assure you
that your baby

180
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:57,900
will be safe for long.

181
00:08:57,967 --> 00:09:01,333
That's why you need strict
bed rest.

182
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:04,600
Avoid everything that
stresses you out

183
00:09:04,667 --> 00:09:07,100
both physically and emotionally.

184
00:09:07,167 --> 00:09:10,867
Or else you will continue
bleeding.

185
00:09:10,933 --> 00:09:12,700
And you might lose your baby.

186
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,667
Please, excuse me.

187
00:09:23,133 --> 00:09:24,100
Excuse me.

188
00:09:24,167 --> 00:09:25,100
Thank you, Doc.

189
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:45,767
You heard what Dr. Villegas
said.

190
00:09:45,833 --> 00:09:48,633
You have to obey Dr. Villegas.

191
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,300
Pregnancy is not that easy.

192
00:09:53,233 --> 00:09:57,967
It's not like a computer
that you can reboot

193
00:09:58,033 --> 00:10:00,833
once it malfunctions.

194
00:10:02,100 --> 00:10:06,000
Your child's life depends
on you.

195
00:10:09,267 --> 00:10:13,867
You must avoid whatever
the reason for your bleeding.

196
00:10:13,933 --> 00:10:17,300
Avoid all negativities.

197
00:10:17,367 --> 00:10:19,400
It won't do you any good.

198
00:10:21,067 --> 00:10:22,367
But...

199
00:10:22,433 --> 00:10:23,467
But what?

200
00:10:25,900 --> 00:10:29,400
Are you still thinking
about your mom?

201
00:10:30,833 --> 00:10:31,867
Let me ask you.

202
00:10:31,933 --> 00:10:34,167
Do you think she's worried
about you?

203
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:38,567
This is all your mom's fault.

204
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,433
Sir.

205
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:43,433
Yes, Ma'am.

206
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:49,067
Where can I ask about
a patient's room?

207
00:10:49,133 --> 00:10:51,333
Maám, just ask over there at the
nurse station.

208
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,767
- Okay, thank you.
- Okay.

209
00:11:05,533 --> 00:11:07,400
Well, you must really love her.

210
00:11:08,567 --> 00:11:09,933
You got her pregnant.

211
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:14,233
So...

212
00:11:14,300 --> 00:11:16,167
something happened
between the two of you.

213
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,700
Since when?

214
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:21,700
Was it when we were
on the island?

215
00:11:23,333 --> 00:11:25,700
You don't need to know
the details, Sab.

216
00:11:25,767 --> 00:11:28,000
Whatever happened between us is
our business.

217
00:11:29,067 --> 00:11:31,700
I just don't know
how to accept this.

218
00:11:32,967 --> 00:11:35,167
As far as I know, I don't have
any responsibility to you.

219
00:11:35,233 --> 00:11:38,167
All I care about is my baby
and Yenyen.

220
00:11:46,333 --> 00:11:48,100
Look, Sab. I'm sorry, okay?

221
00:11:49,167 --> 00:11:50,933
Didn't we already talk
about this?

222
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,633
That we'll just remain friends.

223
00:11:54,533 --> 00:11:56,333
It's not that easy.

224
00:11:58,300 --> 00:12:00,767
It's not easy to let you go,
Red.

225
00:12:03,267 --> 00:12:05,600
But don't worry.

226
00:12:05,667 --> 00:12:07,500
I'll try harder this time.

227
00:12:09,667 --> 00:12:13,067
Congrats on your new journey
with Yenyen.

228
00:12:14,567 --> 00:12:17,267
I'll be here if you need
anything...

229
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,933
as a friend.

230
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:23,567
I'll go ahead.

231
00:12:23,633 --> 00:12:24,900
I'll walk you out.

232
00:12:35,767 --> 00:12:37,633
Your mom doesn't care for you.

233
00:12:38,700 --> 00:12:41,967
She even kicked you out.

234
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:45,900
She's capable of hurting you
and your child.

235
00:12:45,967 --> 00:12:47,933
My grandchild.

236
00:12:49,100 --> 00:12:50,733
She doesn't care for you.

237
00:12:51,867 --> 00:12:59,200
I think your mom would want you
to lose your child.

238
00:13:01,867 --> 00:13:06,000
Because I know she was not happy
when she found out

239
00:13:06,067 --> 00:13:08,433
that you're going to have a baby
with Red.

240
00:13:11,667 --> 00:13:15,333
God forgive me, but I would
rather that you lose that child.

241
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:21,267
I don't want to see the result
of your biggest mistake!

242
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:28,533
Your mom doesn't care for you,
Eden.

243
00:13:31,833 --> 00:13:37,767
Now, I'm saying this
because I care for you.

244
00:13:39,467 --> 00:13:41,633
I care about my grandchild.

245
00:13:46,867 --> 00:13:50,400
If you're going to let your mom
near you,

246
00:13:50,467 --> 00:13:53,833
we don't know
what could happen next.

247
00:13:54,900 --> 00:13:59,033
You might lose your baby.

248
00:14:02,233 --> 00:14:08,500
Remember, I care for you
and my grandchild.

249
00:14:10,967 --> 00:14:12,533
Now, think about this...

250
00:14:14,467 --> 00:14:16,633
What is more important to you?

251
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:25,533
Is it your mom or your baby?

252
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:50,767
- Excuse me, Sir.
- Yes, Ma'am?

253
00:14:52,733 --> 00:14:57,433
Do you know Eden Sta. Maria's
room number?

254
00:14:57,500 --> 00:14:59,300
She's in room 206.

255
00:14:59,733 --> 00:15:00,900
Thank you.

256
00:15:10,300 --> 00:15:12,000
Who told you that you could
come here?

257
00:15:13,267 --> 00:15:14,867
I just want to see my daughter.

258
00:15:14,933 --> 00:15:16,133
I want to talk to her.

259
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,233
Your daughter?

260
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:19,333
You have the nerve to call her
your daughter.

261
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:20,667
You lost your daughter
the moment you kicked her

262
00:15:20,733 --> 00:15:21,900
out of your house.

263
00:15:21,967 --> 00:15:23,200
And you don't have the right
to call her your daughter

264
00:15:23,267 --> 00:15:24,433
since you put her life

265
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:26,067
and my grandchild's life
in danger.

266
00:15:26,133 --> 00:15:27,500
So you should leave now!

267
00:15:27,567 --> 00:15:29,833
Get out of here! Leave!

268
00:15:29,900 --> 00:15:32,267
Why are you stopping me
from seeing her?

269
00:15:32,333 --> 00:15:36,333
Even if you took her in,
nothing would change.

270
00:15:36,433 --> 00:15:37,867
Eden is still my daughter!

271
00:15:37,933 --> 00:15:39,767
- Oh, really?
- So let me see her!

272
00:15:39,833 --> 00:15:42,300
Let me remind you, Amanda.

273
00:15:42,367 --> 00:15:44,567
Eden is in the hospital
right now because of you.

274
00:15:44,633 --> 00:15:46,600
This is all your fault.
You put her life in danger!

275
00:15:46,667 --> 00:15:50,333
You put her life and
my grandchild's life in danger.

276
00:15:50,400 --> 00:15:53,633
And as a grandma, I will never
let anything bad happen

277
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:54,933
to my grandchild!

278
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:57,400
Losing my child is enough!

279
00:15:57,467 --> 00:15:58,633
And now you will harm
my grandchild?

280
00:15:58,700 --> 00:16:00,533
No! I won't let that happen.

281
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,933
You should move on.

282
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,367
You know I have nothing to do
with your son's death.

283
00:16:06,433 --> 00:16:08,700
If you want to file a case
against me, then go ahead!

284
00:16:08,800 --> 00:16:10,267
File a lawsuit!

285
00:16:10,333 --> 00:16:11,967
- Come on!
- Fine.

286
00:16:12,033 --> 00:16:15,367
I didn't mean to hurt Eden!

287
00:16:15,433 --> 00:16:16,333
There you go again!

288
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:17,367
Didn't you mean it?

289
00:16:17,433 --> 00:16:18,833
That's what you always say!

290
00:16:18,900 --> 00:16:19,900
You didn't mean to do it.

291
00:16:19,967 --> 00:16:21,033
You're the victim.

292
00:16:21,100 --> 00:16:21,900
You're innocent.

293
00:16:21,967 --> 00:16:24,167
You're always acting innocent!

294
00:16:24,233 --> 00:16:25,367
Can you hear yourself right now?

295
00:16:25,433 --> 00:16:27,867
I won't buy that line anymore!

296
00:16:27,933 --> 00:16:30,067
And Eden will not believe
whatever you have to say.

297
00:16:30,133 --> 00:16:31,367
So just leave her alone.

298
00:16:31,433 --> 00:16:34,233
I don't care if you believe me
or not.

299
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:36,467
All I care about is Eden.

300
00:16:36,533 --> 00:16:38,200
And what she has to say.

301
00:16:38,267 --> 00:16:39,633
Do you understand?

302
00:16:39,700 --> 00:16:42,333
Don't waste your energy, Amanda.

303
00:16:42,433 --> 00:16:44,133
Save it for something else.

304
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:46,600
Because what I have to say
will make you cry.

305
00:16:46,667 --> 00:16:47,933
The last time I talked to Eden,

306
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:51,500
she told me she didn't want
to see you anymore.

307
00:16:51,567 --> 00:16:53,667
So please, leave.

308
00:16:53,733 --> 00:16:55,533
The door is that way.

309
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:56,300
Go!

310
00:16:56,367 --> 00:16:57,667
I don't believe you.

311
00:16:57,733 --> 00:16:59,467
I know my daughter
would want to see me.

312
00:16:59,533 --> 00:17:01,067
Eden!

313
00:17:01,133 --> 00:17:02,267
- Eden!
- Amanda, stop!

314
00:17:02,333 --> 00:17:03,767
- Amanda!
- Eden!

315
00:17:03,833 --> 00:17:06,967
Why are you forcing
yourself in?

316
00:17:07,033 --> 00:17:08,367
Eden is not well.

317
00:17:08,433 --> 00:17:10,733
Please do her a favor
and just leave!

318
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:12,667
You're annoying.

319
00:17:12,733 --> 00:17:14,200
- You're a pest!
- Eden!

320
00:17:14,267 --> 00:17:15,667
I told you not to go in there!

321
00:17:15,767 --> 00:17:17,833
- You're hurting me!
- You're hurting me too!

322
00:17:17,900 --> 00:17:19,367
Eden!

323
00:17:19,433 --> 00:17:21,667
Guard! Security!

324
00:17:21,733 --> 00:17:23,667
Security!

325
00:17:23,733 --> 00:17:24,733
Amanda! Amanda!

326
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:26,633
What's your problem?

327
00:17:26,700 --> 00:17:27,767
Stop getting in my way!

328
00:17:27,833 --> 00:17:28,733
She's my daughter!

329
00:17:30,833 --> 00:17:31,700
Mom.

330
00:17:31,767 --> 00:17:32,767
Your daughter?

331
00:17:32,833 --> 00:17:34,033
- Yes, she's my daughter.
- You kicked her out.

332
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:35,767
She's still my daughter.

333
00:17:35,833 --> 00:17:37,167
You no longer have the right
to your daughter!

334
00:17:37,233 --> 00:17:39,267
She doesn't want to see you
anymore!

335
00:17:39,333 --> 00:17:40,933
I don't want to see your face!

336
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:43,167
- Security!
- Ma'am.

337
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,333
Mom.

338
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:52,300
Don't listen to that woman!

339
00:17:52,367 --> 00:17:53,667
Can you please make her leave?

340
00:17:53,733 --> 00:17:55,167
Don't believe her.

341
00:17:55,233 --> 00:17:55,967
- Get her out!
- Mom.

342
00:17:56,033 --> 00:17:57,533
- Get her out!
- Mom.

343
00:18:02,967 --> 00:18:03,800
Mom.

344
00:18:04,867 --> 00:18:06,433
Red, I'm begging you.

345
00:18:06,500 --> 00:18:08,133
I want to see Eden.

346
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:09,100
I want to explain.

347
00:18:09,167 --> 00:18:10,667
I didn't mean what happened.

348
00:18:10,733 --> 00:18:14,433
Please, Red.
I want to see my daughter.

349
00:18:14,500 --> 00:18:17,700
Miss Amanda, Yenyen is not fine.

350
00:18:17,767 --> 00:18:19,533
Her pregnancy is very fragile
right now.

351
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:21,733
She can't be stressed.

352
00:18:21,833 --> 00:18:23,067
I'm her mom.

353
00:18:23,133 --> 00:18:24,267
Her mom?

354
00:18:24,333 --> 00:18:25,567
You kicked her
out of your house.

355
00:18:26,667 --> 00:18:27,500
Red.

356
00:18:27,567 --> 00:18:29,000
Eden!

357
00:18:29,067 --> 00:18:32,133
Eden, I'm right here!

358
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:33,967
Tell her to leave.
You're doing the right thing.

359
00:18:36,267 --> 00:18:37,367
- Eden!
- I know what you're thinking!

360
00:18:37,433 --> 00:18:38,867
Don't you dare!

361
00:18:38,933 --> 00:18:40,067
Don't you dare!

362
00:18:40,133 --> 00:18:41,267
I'm her mom.

363
00:18:41,333 --> 00:18:43,233
I just want to see her.

364
00:18:43,300 --> 00:18:44,833
- Come with me.
- Yen!

365
00:18:47,567 --> 00:18:48,533
Yen...

366
00:18:48,600 --> 00:18:51,667
Avoid anything that can
stress you out

367
00:18:51,733 --> 00:18:53,567
both physically and emotionally.

368
00:18:53,633 --> 00:18:57,133
Or else you'll continue
bleeding.

369
00:18:57,233 --> 00:18:58,867
And you might lose your baby.

370
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:04,000
If you let your mom come
near you,

371
00:19:04,067 --> 00:19:07,267
we don't know what could
happen next.

372
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:12,367
You might lose the baby.

373
00:19:20,133 --> 00:19:22,167
- I'm begging you.
- Yen?

374
00:19:22,233 --> 00:19:23,067
Eden?

375
00:19:23,133 --> 00:19:24,767
- Yen!
- Oh, my God!

376
00:19:24,833 --> 00:19:26,033
Look at what happened!

377
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:28,000
I told you she's not well.

378
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:29,700
You're making her
condition worse!

379
00:19:29,767 --> 00:19:30,967
- Can you please leave?
- Eden!

380
00:19:31,033 --> 00:19:32,067
Guard, get her out of here!

381
00:19:32,133 --> 00:19:33,100
Make her leave!

382
00:19:33,167 --> 00:19:33,667
- Get out! Get out!
- You have to leave.

383
00:19:33,767 --> 00:19:35,467
My daughter needs me!

384
00:19:35,533 --> 00:19:38,133
I'll just make sure
she gets out of here.

385
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:41,333
- Get out! Leave!
- My daughter needs me!

386
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:44,200
- Get her out of here!
- Eden, I'm here!

387
00:19:44,267 --> 00:19:47,800
- Let me talk to my daughter!
- Get her away from here!

388
00:19:47,867 --> 00:19:49,067
- Get her out of here!
- Yes, Ma'am.

389
00:19:49,133 --> 00:19:50,900
Get her out of here!

390
00:19:50,967 --> 00:19:53,733
Leave! Get out!

391
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:54,800
- Get her out!
- Please, Ma'am.

392
00:19:54,867 --> 00:19:55,967
You have to leave.

393
00:19:57,267 --> 00:20:00,167
Guard, make sure that she
won't come back here.

394
00:20:00,233 --> 00:20:01,900
- Yes, Ma'am.
- You can't do this to me!

395
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:02,933
You don't have the right
to do this!

396
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:04,100
You monster!

397
00:20:04,167 --> 00:20:05,667
You're calling me a monster?
You're the monster!

398
00:20:05,733 --> 00:20:06,967
You saw Eden's condition.

399
00:20:07,033 --> 00:20:08,433
And you're still forcing
your way in?

400
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:10,267
Don't you feel guilty?

401
00:20:10,333 --> 00:20:13,300
You put my grandchild's life
in danger!

402
00:20:13,367 --> 00:20:15,500
I didn't mean to do that!

403
00:20:15,567 --> 00:20:16,533
It's not my fault!

404
00:20:16,600 --> 00:20:17,700
I need to talk to my daughter.

405
00:20:17,767 --> 00:20:18,933
I need to explain to her.

406
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,700
You don't have the right
to do this to me!

407
00:20:20,767 --> 00:20:22,333
You can't stop me!

408
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:24,233
Try to come back here.

409
00:20:24,300 --> 00:20:26,833
And I will have you
dragged back to jail!

410
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:28,267
Don't let her inside!

411
00:20:28,333 --> 00:20:30,400
- Yes, Ma'am.
- Let me see the title!

412
00:20:30,467 --> 00:20:31,533
Close the door!

413
00:20:31,600 --> 00:20:33,767
- Don't let her in!
- Yes, Ma'am.

414
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:38,267
I told you you're on bed rest.

415
00:20:38,367 --> 00:20:41,167
You can't get out of bed.

416
00:20:41,233 --> 00:20:44,400
You can't get stressed,
or else...

417
00:20:44,467 --> 00:20:47,267
I heard my mom outside.

418
00:20:47,333 --> 00:20:49,867
She came here to cause trouble.

419
00:20:49,933 --> 00:20:51,700
Look at what happened.

420
00:20:51,767 --> 00:20:54,267
You almost got hurt again.

421
00:20:54,333 --> 00:20:55,800
I'm sorry, Auntie.

422
00:20:55,867 --> 00:20:56,800
It's okay.

423
00:20:56,867 --> 00:20:58,567
It's not your fault, okay?

424
00:21:00,167 --> 00:21:01,533
Thank you, Doctor.

425
00:21:03,367 --> 00:21:07,067
If you want to keep your
child alive, Eden,

426
00:21:07,133 --> 00:21:07,933
you have to be obedient.

427
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:09,300
You have to be strong.

428
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:11,833
Don't be stubborn, okay?

429
00:21:13,333 --> 00:21:15,367
I know you want to see your mom.

430
00:21:15,433 --> 00:21:17,000
But right now...

431
00:21:17,067 --> 00:21:19,200
she can't do anything
to help you.

432
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:26,533
I'm not saying this
because I'm mad at her.

433
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:29,233
Our feud has nothing
to do with this.

434
00:21:31,367 --> 00:21:35,267
I'm saying this because
I care for you

435
00:21:35,333 --> 00:21:37,100
and my grandchild.

436
00:21:38,133 --> 00:21:41,333
I know what's best
for all of us.

437
00:21:49,233 --> 00:21:52,133
I will call the cops on Amanda

438
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:53,533
if she doesn't stop
bothering us.

439
00:21:53,600 --> 00:21:55,933
I will file a case
against her and put her...

440
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:56,867
No, Auntie!

441
00:21:56,933 --> 00:21:58,533
I don't want her to go to jail.

442
00:21:58,600 --> 00:22:01,367
Eden, if I don't do it,
she won't learn her lesson.

443
00:22:01,433 --> 00:22:02,933
Where's that witch?

444
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:04,667
I'm following her around.

445
00:22:04,733 --> 00:22:06,033
She's walking by herself.

446
00:22:06,100 --> 00:22:09,367
Now I want to see how far
she can go.

447
00:22:09,433 --> 00:22:11,733
What do you want me to do?

448
00:22:11,800 --> 00:22:19,000
I want to drain her strength
until she can't fight anymore.
